{"tid":1157013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺韓國瑜競選既路線根本就係抄楊秋興","createTime":"2019-05-16T03:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T03:59:36.000Z","uid":212509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9948c2d1c812c50a9bde7f4d98673019a037b01","tid":1157013,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:35:15.000Z","msg":"唔知大家知唔知邊個係楊秋興<br />\n佢曾經係民進黨高雄縣縣長，係2010高雄縣同高雄市合併成直轄市之後，就同陳菊爭民進黨出選高雄市長既資格。<br />\n輸咗之後就退黨獨立參選，結果就輸到仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後加入國民黨，2014年選多一次，又係輸到仆街。<br />\n上年就幫韓國瑜助選，有份幫佢入主高雄市。<br />\n但選舉過後韓就用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個位都冇安排比楊秋興係市政府做。<br />\n最近國民黨爭緊總統出選資格，楊秋興就轉為幫郭台銘，仲話如果當日知道韓國瑜咁快就選總統既話一定唔會幫佢，結果比韓粉屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家藍綠兩邊都笑佢係背骨仔<br />\n但其實韓國瑜先係踩住楊秋興上位嗰個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxRrUw6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxRrUw6.jpg&h=94d30d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜話自己係高雄ceo,但其實呢個宣傳手法一早比楊秋興用過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBO595K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBO595K.jpg&h=ad1687d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用負面手法宣傳自己，「高雄又老又窮」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAbfNSF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAbfNSF.jpg&h=53549756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打造高雄，xxxx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339491c1e0b695f0c70a8f3faea8edc20f8d0d25","tid":1157013,"uid":138197,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"多口問句 你咁關心台灣政治做乜 關我地撚事咩"},{"pid":"dba705b9bf56b6962af8c2d104ff0d9ccd7ee3f2","tid":1157013,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:42:37.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜去澳門選特首<br />\n口號&quot;發大財&quot;"},{"pid":"7de9fb4b822eda48cdca5dc97be1fca63f0d3d0c","tid":1157013,"uid":107405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"韓國魚個鄉下佬形象做得似過佢 因為本人真係無乜腦又乜撚都唔識<br />\n而且撞著呢期高雄經濟狀況差 綠黨人氣大跌<br />\n時勢造狗熊 只可以講楊秋興揀錯時機入場"},{"pid":"b26dfb0743701885b991ae1eb6edb5d52761b0d2","tid":1157013,"uid":1372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"背骨一時爽，一直背骨一直爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609af056d8e0d84153c05df062f843826e5020c3","tid":1157013,"uid":212509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6uX1nQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6uX1nQ.jpg&h=6de66a1b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}